# The `AttributeSet` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

## Description {#details}

This class holds the attributes for a particular argument, parameter, function, or return value.

It is an immutable value type that is cheap to copy. Adding and removing enum attributes is intended to be fast, but adding and removing string or integer attributes involves a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/foldingset">FoldingSet</a> lookup.
